Show HN: I taught an AI to see the future
text:
Hey everyone,
In these uncertain times, Future News is an AI system that gives us a glimpse into the future. It is explicitly prohibited from predicting war or environmental disaster, instead encouraging us towards positive outcomes. I am compiling a training document for fine-tuning with the intention that Future News makes increasingly accurate predictions over time.
